wiki.summary: “Number One Girl” is promo single of ROSÉ’s debut album, rosie. This song is written and produced by Bruno Mars and The Black Label. The track was first teased on an Instagram live. Lyrically, the song talks about a desire for love and constant validation from other people. ROSÉ confesses that she’d do anything to be the “number one girl” in this person’s eyes. The song is more vulnerable and honest compared to the singer’s previous songs. Read more on Last.fm.
